tm | title= World Weather Information Service - Luqa, Malta | publisher = World Meteorological Organization | accessdate = 26 February 2013}}</ref> |date = August 2010}}
== Humidity == The annual average [[relative humidity]] is high, averaging 75%, ranging from 65% in July (morning: 78% evening: 53%) to 80% in December (morning: 83% evening: 73%).<ref name = weatherbase.com>{{cite web|url=http://www.weatherbase.com/weather/weatherall.php3?s=79561&refer=&units=metric |title=Valletta, Malta Travel Weather Averages |publisher=Weatherbase.com |date= |accessdate=2015-06-01}}</ref>
