==[[Parakou]]== *[[Hopital Ahmadiyya Parakou]]<ref>http://ahmadiyyabenin.org {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20150416164519/http://ahmadiyyabenin.org/ |date=2015-04-16 }}</ref> *[[Parakou Hospital]]<ref name="Sargent1989">{{cite book|last=Sargent|first=Carolyn Fishel|title=Maternity, medicine, and power: reproductive decisions in urban Benin|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ofDatylMrNwC&pg=PA48|accessdate=27 November 2011|year=1989|publisher=University of California Press|isbn=978-0-520-06484-3|page=48}}</ref>
